{
  "texts": [
    "Both of these codes have a distance d = 2 using n = 4 physical qubits.",
    "The two codes differ by the number of logical qubits they each encode.",
    "The [[4, 2, 2]] code encodes k = 2 logical qubits and the [[4, 1, 2]] code encodes k = 1 logical qubit.The theory of code deformations.",
    "We inject a state into a larger code 11,[19][20][21][22][23][24][25][26]41,52 using code deformation 19,46,53.",
    "In what follows, we describe the theory of code deformations using the stabilizer formalism."
  ]
}